---
// A headshot or drone-in-hand photo (public/images/about.jpg) can be added to
// this section later if Jacob wants a face to go with the story.
---

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container about-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="kicker">About</p>
      <h2>Rooted in Pittsburgh,<br />focused from above</h2>
      <p>
        I'm Jacob Poteet, the pilot and photographer behind Three Rivers Aerial Co.
        I've always loved aviation and photography, and this business is where the
        two finally come together. Every flight is a chance to see a familiar place
        from a new angle and capture it at its best.
      </p>
      <p>
        I work with realtors, brokers, developers, and homeowners across the Greater
        Pittsburgh area, from the South Hills to the North Shore and from Sewickley
        estates to Strip District commercial blocks. Every flight is FAA Part 107
        certified with airspace clearance handled before takeoff, and I take pride in
        giving my clients a seamless experience that elevates their listing from the
        first call to final delivery.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-gold">Work With Me</a>
    </div>
    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat">
        <strong>68%</strong>
        <span>of listings with aerial media sell faster than those without</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <strong>72hr</strong>
        <span>standard turnaround from flight to final delivery</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <strong>100%</strong>
        <span>FAA-compliant flights with airspace clearance secured</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about .btn { margin-top: 0.75rem; }

  .stats {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .stat {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--gold-500);
    padding: 0.5rem 0 0.5rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .stat strong {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .stat span {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--stone-dim);
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  }
</style>
